title: Europa League: Juergen Klopp fails to inspire Liverpool in stalemate
text: Jurgen Klopp 'Looking Forward' to Anfield Debut 01:09 The German coach will take charge in front of a home crowd for the first time as Liverpool boss when they take on Rubin Kazan in the Europa League. Klopp encouraged the home crowd to get involved and cheer on the Reds. Recent related news Juergen Klopp had warned Liverpool fans he had no stardust to sprinkle on the squad and Thursday's display proved him right.
